{"tid":1383614,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"超級優惠價提供中午晚比年青及學生！！","createTime":"2019-07-29T17:27:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T16:39:08.000Z","uid":121655,"like":25,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"284f93aa22495ee07b20212a4f753dee404c663e","tid":1383614,"uid":121655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T17:27:32.000Z","msg":"諗到多一個方案 <br />\n就係年輕人或者係學生<span style=\"color: gold;\">（弱勢社群）</span><br />\n餐廳搞折搞優惠 <br />\n早午晚 全面支持關心 比愛年青人<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">半價 或者 更平</span><br />\n咁當然都要賺錢 唔係蝕本生意！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">希望各界大型既 中小企 用行動去支持年青人！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n唔係口講又唔做！咪撚做錄音機！"},{"pid":"15034f4f8cd9d7bbfb0257c99e23668590b693da","tid":1383614,"uid":121655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T17:28:15.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">做個良心企業！</span></span>"},{"pid":"bd8e19718b762f4b7211288d64139aaee4550d30","tid":1383614,"uid":121655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T17:28:45.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">認同幫推上熱門</span></span>"},{"pid":"ae8eeb92a3826d7e4038471acde8b468aa1e4827","tid":1383614,"uid":121655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T17:29:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"06fb9e5243db9097a571b0ee4858991e8c1ffb57","tid":1383614,"uid":121655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T17:29:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"672e8bc3102c19bb1cf67848ebd0dcac8e58d13c","tid":1383614,"uid":121655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T17:29:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3a76f589d30c39d6996e5111fd8f8a320f3248a6","tid":1383614,"uid":121655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T17:29:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bbc33181c3fa8bea3f277caab1bf89e5d26a0394","tid":1383614,"uid":121655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score